---
title: Panko-Crusted Chicken & Lemon Sauce with Cherry Tomato Salad
description: There’s nothing quite like the golden crust of a good old-fashioned crusted chicken breast to cheer you up – that’s just simple science. And as for condiments? We think our lemon sauce might just make for the ultimate finishing touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b721553ae08b54cfc0442f2-b2fb71a5.jpg
